Package: raum
Type: Package
Title:  Risk Adjusted Underwriting Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@: c(person("Seokhoon", "Joo", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "seokhoonj@gmail.com"))
Date: 2022-02-22
Description: A virtual loss ratio simulation is performed based on the claim cohort data and 
             an adjusted underwriting model is established according to the result of the simulation.
             The model considers disease codes and risk rates.
